{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act51side", "eventName": "人们，我们", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PA-4", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "一墙之隔", "storyInfo": "听证会上，娜塔莉娅的“忏悔信”详述了她的见闻：她与巴普洛维奇协商后，见到了索尼娅并得知了封锁区里的情况。索尼娅希望娜塔莉娅她们能想办法切断暴徒们的武装供应。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g13_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必须重申一次，孩子。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你只是来还书，仍不愿考虑我先前的建议，那么你可以把书放在那边的壁炉上，然后离开。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难道只要我不同意您的办法，您就真的连一句旁的话也不愿和我说了吗？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放在其他时候，即使你因着年轻人可爱的轻率做出再多糊涂的选择，我都能继续同你促膝长谈，直到深夜。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毕竟，我的确错过了许多。关于你，关于你父母，关于你们在切城的经历......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "现在我同样能将这些都告诉您。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可现在我却没有资格去听。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面对关乎生死的问题，我无法说服你接受我的安排——离开圣骏堡避避风头，或者至少提交一份对自己有利无害的证词。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我无法保护你，也就无颜面对你的父母，那我又有什么资格从你这里了解有关他们的任何事情？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#16$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是这样的，夫人——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#16$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这本书，你读了吗？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我读了，我全都读了，我已经明白您为什么要将它借给我。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的扉页上写着什么？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“世上没有任何主义，值得人们用美好的生活去交换。”", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，是的。雅科夫·彼得洛夫的《忏悔录》，在他死后由其家人整理出版，一本背叛者用死亡换来的经验之谈。所以，我真的不明白......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你知道已经有人为这经验付出过生命的代价，而自己还能有所选择，那又为何......一定要重蹈覆辙呢？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难道一定要在你行将就木，甚至是像他一样在牢狱中咽下鲜血的时候，你才能意识到自己所坚信的只是注定被历史遗忘的瞬间？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人，我......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告诉我吧，孩子，告诉我为什么。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......说实在的，我也问过我自己。可如果......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "请原谅我的厚颜无耻，我还想提一个要求。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我能按照您的办法出具这份证词，保全自己，您能答应我，对自治团里的其他成员也一视同仁吗？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然！只要你能按那些人想要的，在证词里列出特定人员的名字——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。那么，我会做的。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我会向听证会提交一份这样的证词......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一封“忏悔信”。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯爵夫人？", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，我在听。你想说什么？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我想提醒您，仲裁人刚才提到娜塔莉娅小姐了，一会儿需要您把她的证词递上去。", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一位证人，娜塔莉娅·罗斯托娃小姐。出于特殊原因，她本人今日不会出席。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，她已提前申请，由现场某位人士代为诵读证词。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仲裁人阁下——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅小姐在昨日将信件交付于我，请仲裁委员会诸位大人过目，并允许我诵读。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当书记官接过苦艾手中的信件时，窃窃私议的声音越来越大，沃伦佐娃夫人感到无数目光汇集于自身，她摇了摇头。"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，请卓娅女士代为讲述娜塔莉娅小姐在此事中的见闻。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“公正的仲裁委员会，以及受人敬仰的诸位大人，这是一封忏悔信......”", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“出于我的悔意，与这封信所涉及的敏感之事，除了不得不谈论的巴普洛维奇外，我不会提及任何大人的具体姓名。”", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）夫人，这和我们说的——", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先听她念完吧。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“......我希望，这足以换取诸位的信任。”", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“在舞会事件发生后不久，出于对索尼娅安危的深切忧虑，我托一位有影响力的人士帮忙，成功联系到了当天大多数被捕学生的家长。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“我得知，所有擅闯萨列夫格勒区的‘罪犯’，都将被统一关押在卡托加区，也就是现在人们口中的‘封锁区’。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“令我意外的是，尽管家长中不乏地位显赫的贵族，他们也难以获得封锁区内的确切消息。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“其中一部分人，是考虑到自身身份敏感，不便直接涉足封锁区。于是，他们委托我作为所有人的代表，前往探视被捕学生。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“他们向我推荐了封锁区的管理者——枢密官巴普洛维奇。为拜访他，隔日我便登上了隔绝卡托加区与外界的城墙。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈，我还见了一位您父亲的朋友，舒瓦洛夫男爵，当初他举债跑到切尔诺伯格搞投资，后来又一穷二白地回到圣骏堡。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_saw_n_1", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但前天我们见面时，他被铐着双手，正由两位警官押着出城，要往东边送。我好奇问他，这是犯了多大的事儿，还要被流放？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他神秘兮兮地凑到我耳边说，参加宴会的时候，他喊了一句“矿工万岁”。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我惊讶地问他为什么，您猜他说什么？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我猜不出来。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他笑着回头，看向那两个押送他的警官，说：“被流放了，债主就找不到我了，哈哈哈哈。”", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这真是，特别的见闻......如果我没有要事在身，或许听一天都不会疲惫。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧我，一闲聊就停不下来，真是让您见笑了。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "来，亲爱的罗斯托娃小姐。我们先说正事。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枢密官阁下，我是为——", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_saw_n_2", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尖厉的电钻声彻底搅扰了巴普洛维奇的兴致，他略带歉意地向早露挥手，起身走到门边。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么搞的？今天谁管事？给我出来！", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#8$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对不起大人，昨晚带回来的人比较多......", "name": "“十六勇士”打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我管你有多少人？不知道我正在招待客人吗？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#8$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我这就让他们停手。", "name": "“十六勇士”打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，我们刚才说到哪儿了？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原谅我的好奇，枢密官阁下。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圣骏堡各区的军警都有统一的装备，而刚刚与您交谈的那个人拿着武器，却身着便服。这里有什么特殊之处吗？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特殊？哈哈，罗斯托娃小姐说笑了，除非您觉得垃圾场也很特殊。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在圣骏堡工业转型升级后，老的工业区闲置久了，就有议员提出，可以把这些地方都改造一下，再利用起来。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如用来关些罪犯和一些不愿搬迁的穷人，在封锁区内就地搞生产，一举多得。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本来运转得好好的，如果不是这几个月资源吃紧，这些工厂也不会全都停工。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，乌萨斯从来不会在无用之处多费心思。正规的军警数量有限，给我的资金也只够雇这种白痴帮我管理。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "万幸的是，这些家伙至今为止还没有出过岔子。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那刚才的钻头声，似乎也不是在装修——", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，如果让您受惊的话，很抱歉。那是牙医在做手术，我也不愿他惊扰到我宝贵的客人。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牙医？在这里？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，他们要钻开虫蛀之处，把烂掉的东西挖出来，填上新的材料......无论是牙齿，还是思想。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信罗斯托娃小姐的好奇心已经得到满足了，我们该来谈正事了吧？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......实在抱歉。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刚见面时，您看过我给的名单，我是受他们父母的委托而来，希望您能让我确认这些人的情况。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其考虑到那名单之中不乏达官显贵的继承人，还请枢密官阁下通融。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然，当然。这次被捕的确实好像都是学生，可怜天下父母心，我当然知道那些大人物对自己的继承人有多么关切。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这些孩子要是能够体谅半点他们父母的心思，又怎么会做出这种大逆不道、令父母伤心的事呢？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可您也该体谅，我对于卡托加区的未来有多么关切。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枢密官阁下，在与您进一步谈判前我得再次申明，委托我来的家长们希望能够确认孩子们的状态。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然，当然，一会儿有的是时间让您慢慢确认他们的安危。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是那份名单上有两个名字，我还想和罗斯托娃小姐讨论讨论。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您请说。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先是瑙姆。据我所知，他已经在昨日被释放了，或许在您来的路上，他就已经到家了。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感谢您的告知，我会尽快和他的家长确认。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，其次就是这位——索尼娅。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "短短几天她便在这里名声大噪，我也从手下那里了解到了不少有关她的事迹。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索尼娅怎么了？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看着巴普洛维奇惯常挂在脸上的微笑，娜塔莉娅突然感觉到一丝异样。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别紧张，我只是好奇，她既非贵族，也不是富有人家的孩子，只是个普通学生，究竟为何能够出现在这份名单上呢？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我无意隐瞒。只因为索尼娅是我的朋友，并非什么真正穷凶极恶的暴徒，所以我才加上了她的名字，恳请您能让我确认她的情况。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，天哪。罗斯托夫家的继承人向我求助，我怎么会拒绝呢？", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，您必须答应我两件事：其一，您告诉索尼娅，让她这几日安心留在封锁区里，我保证过几日就放她出去。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其二，去依次告诉名单上学生们的家长，让他们向议会施压，撤回提案，保留封锁区，无论用什么手段。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“保留”封锁区？您是指，卡托加区的区划很快就会被撤销？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，小姐，我们亲爱的沃伦佐娃夫人竟然没有告诉您吗？这里面对的可不是简单的撤销......而是赤裸裸的放弃。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝国资源枯竭已经不是什么秘密了。为了节流，帝国甚至已经窘迫到要放弃一块位于首都的工业地块。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早在一周前，议会就有了放弃封锁区，将它抛在荒野上的提案。这提案得到了议长的许可，也就代表着陛下的默认。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸运的是，在一些支持我的旧贵族的力保下，这件事的推行得以拖延至今。但这不是长久之计。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我注意到您的名单中有不少知名的产业贵族，倘若他们能鼓动各自亲友一同反对，想必陛下和议会也得重新考量。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这关乎他们孩子的性命，他们绝不敢怠慢。一旦收到保留封锁区的敕令，我就放所有人离开。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您认为我能做到？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少我对您抱有期待。凭您拿到了这份名单，毫无畏惧地来到这个人人避之不及的地方，还想救您的朋友。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，包括索尼娅在内，所有人的性命都在您手上了，娜塔莉娅·罗斯托娃小姐。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我会转达的，但首先，我要见到索尼娅。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“小松针”，过来。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "带这位小姐去见索尼娅吧，记得要报上娜塔莉娅的名号。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g4_blockst", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormlp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......这儿离那家伙——离索尼娅的驻地不远，你先等着，我去通报。", "name": "被雇佣的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在这里已经有驻地了？还需要“通报”？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是她的朋友，那肯定知道，她确实是个不好对付的家伙。", "name": "被雇佣的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露的嘴角不禁有了一丝笑意。阴冷的街道深处吹来一阵风，她扶住帽子，侧过头去。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然，一道灰影从废墟里窜出。那是只瘦骨嶙峋的云兽，浑身癞斑，它停在路中间，警惕地看向早露，嘴里死死叼着一截东西。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露的瞳孔骤然收缩——那是一根人的手指，苍白、僵硬，指甲缝里嵌着黑泥与血污，断口处像是被嚼碎的树枝。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickbeat"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*乌萨斯粗口*！该死的畜生！", "name": "被雇佣的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smallanimal_scream"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅小姐，你没事吧？", "name": "被雇佣的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......没事，它刚才......不，没什么。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街道上实在有些冷，得麻烦您尽快请索尼娅出来了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "马上。", "name": "被雇佣的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2166_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看着打手逐渐消失的背影，一阵寒颤从头打到脚，早露原本挺直的身躯猛地软了下来。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "yTo": 20.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她跌跌撞撞，最后倚在冰冷的砖墙上，捂住了嘴巴。将喉头的动静强行咽下之后，泪水却不受控制地涌出眼眶。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.61, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一根指头，一个屈辱的灵魂的尖叫，一片关于切尔诺伯格的、浑噩的记忆，全都疯狂涌进少女的脑海。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这不是她第一次经历，她能够独自面对——"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不能这样，娜塔莉娅。这是不体面的，是不被允许的，是能被克服的。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g4_blockst", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露蹲在地上，大口地呼吸着金属味道的冷空气，试图先让手臂停止颤抖......"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rapidbreath_female", "loop": "true", "channel": "1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rapidbreath_female", "loop": "true", "channel": "2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.9, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.2}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.61, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "2", "fadetime": 0.8}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "loop": "true", "channel": "zl", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "zl", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "zl", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅？", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_heartbeat", "volume": 0.7, "channel": "HB", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "HB", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "em", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "em", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rapidbreath_female", "loop": "true", "channel": "3", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "3", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（艰难地呼吸）", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "凛冬", "content": "你过呼吸了——"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "凛冬", "content": "该死！娜塔莉娅，你能听到我说话吗？"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rapidbreath_female", "loop": "true", "channel": "4", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 0.0, "channel": "4"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "4", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "em", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#16$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#16$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告诉我，你现在在哪儿？", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#16$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在......我在......封锁区......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对，你在封锁区——*乌萨斯粗口*你们一个两个的，到底进来做什么？找死吗？", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......该死，现在不该说这个。听我说，娜塔莉娅。我在你身边，你不是一个人。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅！", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索尼娅......？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对，是我。你还好吗？", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索尼娅......不，我没事，很高兴看到你......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也没事。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么还是语无伦次的。这是几？", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬伸出三个手指，戳到早露面前。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，至少脑子没问题。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我没事，只是吹了风，咳嗽起来，心脏就有点难受。现在已经好很多了，谢谢你。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，在我面前就别装了。是不是刚才来找我那家伙惹你了？", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的不是......唉，算了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "听着，索尼娅，我能在这里停留的时间有限，必须尽快把目前的情况都告诉你。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她四下打量，朝凛冬示意，希望她靠得更近些。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了，你是从管事的人那过来的。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先告诉你一声，烈夏目前也在这里，你还需要知道什么吗？", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罗莎琳......她一直坚持要来找你，只在办事处留下封信就走了。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要责怪她，她也只是急着来帮我......我，我想问问大家都怎么样了？", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古米还好吗？真理她有没有生我的气？还有卓娅和教官她们......", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家很好，但每个人都在担心你。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我过来也是想确认你的安全，以及这片封锁区......", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你看到了什么，但这里发生的事，大概比你在这么短时间内看到的还要糟上不少。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有食物，没有燃料，甚至没有干净的饮用水。不同的人在拉帮结派，四处争斗，抢夺地盘和资源。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天都有人死。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴普洛维奇说他会放所有人离开，只是有些条件——", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不会真相信这种人说的话吧？", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我当然不......", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你也没有别的办法，否则不会还要到处求人才能进来，还只能告诉我消息，看看我怎么样。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么说呢，虽然刚才我说的好像很恐怖，仿佛明天大家就都玩完了，但这对我们来说并不陌生......", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一片哪怕明天就爆炸也没人在意的封锁区域，一群为生存相互倾碾得几乎只剩下本能的学生......", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这里的一切都有种熟悉的感觉，是不是？", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......告诉我，你现在需要什么？我还能离开这里，出去之后，我们这些在外面的人都会想办法——", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要知道，这圈和堡垒一样的城墙上面有多少人？除了那些混混。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很少，巴普洛维奇请了几名保镖，加上穿旧款军队制服的那些也不超过十人。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不错。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬往早露的方向靠得更近，迫切地压低了声音。"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）如果可能的话，尽量想办法切断他们的武装供应。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）武装？可我看到他们的“安保人员”都不是专业的。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）不，你不知道。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）最近这里每天都有弹药补给和重型武器运进来，要是每个高地都有那样的大家伙守着，我们根本没有对抗的可能。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是......", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是字面意思。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白了，出去后我会和大家商量，一起想想办法。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索尼娅，你和罗莎琳都要保重，一定要保护好自己。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别担心，我会出去的，会带着大家一起出去。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像以前一样。", "name": "凛冬"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}